/#
 The type of update to a record in a report.
 #/
enum FpML5.reporting.UpdateTypeEnum {
    # The item is newly created since the last instance of this report.
    Created 
    # The item has been updated since the last instance of this report.
    Modified 
    # The item has been removed since the last version of this report.
    Deleted 

}

Created.Doc: The item is newly created since the last instance of this report.
Created.Name: Created

Modified.Doc: The item has been updated since the last instance of this report.
Modified.Name: Modified

Deleted.Doc: The item has been removed since the last version of this report.
Deleted.Name: Deleted
